@baseUrl = https://localhost:54666

### Create booking
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingDate": "2026-03-22T10:00:00Z",
  "seatCount": 3,
  "destination": {
    "name": "Conference Center",
    "address": "123 Main St, City"
  },
  "flightId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111"
}

### Capture booking ID from response
@bookingId = {{response.body.id}}

### Get booking by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/ca8817f5-6c81-42a4-9e34-bd1e695e1ffc

### Get bookings by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/bydaterange?startDate=2026-03-01&endDate=2026-03-30